when she's behaving like this?

895
00:48:21,312 --> 00:48:23,245
That's all.

896
00:48:23,348 --> 00:48:25,109
[NORMAL TONE] Listen, I gotta--

897
00:48:25,212 --> 00:48:26,213
I gotta go.

898
00:48:26,317 --> 00:48:27,663
Don't say anything, all right?
- All right.

899
00:48:27,766 --> 00:48:28,560
You take care.

900
00:48:28,664 --> 00:48:29,561
All right.

901
00:48:33,358 --> 00:48:35,326
Renee, can we talk a minute?

