of official record,

1030
00:54:47,629 --> 00:54:50,459
you're going to
look like an idiot.

1031
00:54:50,563 --> 00:54:51,460
All right.

1032
00:54:51,564 --> 00:54:52,427
Thank you, Jesus.

1033
00:54:57,984 --> 00:54:58,778
Now what are you doing?

1034
00:54:58,881 --> 00:55:00,538
[typewriter clacking]

1035
00:55:00,642 --> 00:55:01,953
Making it unofficial.

1036
00:55:02,057 --> 00:55:07,165
Memo to Captain Kirkwood,
from Joe Stachula

1037
00:55:07,269 --> 00:55:08,857
You aren't going to
believe this one.

1038
00:55:19,316 --> 00:55:20,213
Well, I'll be.

1039
00:55:26,219 --> 00:55:27,772
What's up?

1040
00:55:27,876 --> 00:55:29,360
Schuster lives two
blocks away from Terry

1041
00:55:29,464 --> 00:55:32,984
Deveroux's apartment,
and he's got a rap sheet.

1042
00:55:33,088 --> 00:55:34,123
Yeah, sure.

1043
00:55:34,227 --> 00:55:35,470
I understand.

1044
00:55:35,573 --> 00:55:39,646
April 23, I was, uh, right
here, watching the Cubs game.

1045
00:55:39,750 --> 00:55:41,303
I never miss one.

1046
00:55:41,407 --> 00:55:44,410
Yeah, that's right, huh, Yvonne?

1047
00:55:44,513 --> 00:55:45,618
That's right.

1048
00:55:45,721 --> 00:55:46,653
ADAM: Yes, it is.

1049
00:55:46,757 --> 00:55:48,448
I remember because
it was the next day

1050
00:55:48,552 --> 00:55:52,072
