was murdered, so that kind of--

1051
00:55:52,176 --> 00:55:54,143
thanks, honey-- that kind of
imprints things on your mind.

1052
00:55:54,247 --> 00:55:55,559
Do you recall
who won that game?

1053
00:55:55,662 --> 00:55:56,491
No.

1054
00:55:56,594 --> 00:55:59,045
You see, that-- that, I forget.

1055
00:55:59,148 --> 00:56:01,047
You remember that, Yvonne?

1056
00:56:01,150 --> 00:56:02,566
Who won that Cubs game?

1057
00:56:02,669 --> 00:56:03,463
Beats me.

1058
00:56:03,567 --> 00:56:04,775
I hate baseball.

1059
00:56:04,878 --> 00:56:06,259
There you go.

1060
00:56:06,363 --> 00:56:07,640
What is it with the women?

1061
00:56:07,743 --> 00:56:09,158
Every time I sit down
and watch a game,

1062
00:56:09,262 --> 00:56:10,919
