1065
00:56:13,922 --> 00:56:15,302
[chuckles]

1066
00:56:17,097 --> 00:56:19,928
Yvonne, when's the baby due?

1067
00:56:20,031 --> 00:56:20,929
Any day now.

1068
00:56:21,032 --> 00:56:22,551
That's terrific.

1069
00:56:22,655 --> 00:56:24,622
We'll call you if
we need you again.

